Repeat: Purl 2 wrapping the yarn twice for each stitch; k6
Slip 2 wyib dropping the extra wraps; k6
Purl 1 wrapping the yarn twice; sl 2 wyif; Purl 1 wrapping the yarn twice; k4

Slip 3 wyib dropping the extra wrap from the third stitch.  Drop the first elongated Color A stitch off the needle to the front of the work.  Slip the same three stitches back to the left-hand needle.  Pick up the dropped stitch and knit it.  Then k2, sl 1 wyib, dropping the second elongated Color A stitch off the needle to the front of the work.  Slip 3 wyib dropping the extra wrap from the first stitch.  Pick up the dropped stitch and place it on the left-hand needle.  Then slip 2 (the second and the third stitches) back to the left-hand needle, then knit 3.
Purl 1 wrapping the yarn twice; sl 2 wyif; Purl 1 wrapping the yarn twice; k4

Slip 3 wyib dropping the extra wrap from the third stitch.  Drop the first elongated Color A stitch off the needle to the front of the work.  Slip the same three stitches back to the left-hand needle.  Pick up the dropped stitch and knit it.  Then k2, sl 1 wyib, dropping the second elongated Color A stitch off the needle to the front of the work.  Slip 3 wyib dropping the extra wrap from the first stitch.  Pick up the dropped stitch and place it on the left-hand needle.  Then slip 2 (the second and the third stitches) back to the left-hand needle, then knit 3.
